description:
Ange is the first imperial princess of the Misurugi Empire, she was loved by her people as Princess Angelize. After realizing that she is a Norma, she becomes a soldier that fights with dragons and changes her name to Ange. As she was raised as a princess, she has a large amount of pride and is very stubborn. Within the base, she often gets into conflicts with others.
Source: ANN
name: Ange
